I have also since realised that without having access to the Multibanco network, doing business will be far too much effort (forcing me to visit segurança social in person to make payments, for example). I will soon be moving all my banking to a traditional bank, which is something I am loathe to do. I would consider using rauva again in the future but it seems your tech is much further away from where your marketing suggests it is. The only positive I can think of is the support team, who were great whenever I raised an issue.
